  <!-- ============================================================
       Credit-check cases: OTC-011 to OTC-013
       Sequence: Create Order -> Check Credit -> Approve Order ->
                 Pick Items -> Ship Items -> Issue Invoice ->
                 Receive Payment -> Close Order
       ============================================================ -->

  <trace>
